Cc: v4l-dvb maintainer list <v4l-dvb-maintainer@linuxtv.org>, Steven Toth <stoth@linuxtv.org>, Devin Heitmueller <devin.heitmueller@gmail.com>, Mauro Carvalho Chehab <mchehab@redhat.com>
